params.implementation_: The address of the new implementation for delegation

NewAdmin(address,address).notice: Emitted when pendingAdmin is accepted, which means admin is updated

ProposalCanceled(uint256).notice: An event emitted when a proposal has been canceled

ProposalCreated(uint256,address,address[.notice: An event emitted when a new proposal is created

ProposalExecuted(uint256).notice: An event emitted when a proposal has been executed in the Timelock

ProposalQueued(uint256,uint256).notice: An event emitted when a proposal has been queued in the Timelock

ProposalThresholdSet(uint256,uint256).notice: Emitted when proposal threshold is set

_acceptInitialAdminDelegated().notice: Called by the admin to make a delegate call for the acceptInitialAdmin function

_initiateDelegated().notice: Called by the admin to make a delegate call for the initiate function

_setImplementation(address).notice: Called by the admin to update the implementation of the delegator

_setPendingAdminDelegated(address).notice: Called by the admin to make a delegate call for the setPendingAdmin function
